<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ed70145-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s287p"><num value="287p">§ 287p.</num><heading> Citizenship of members</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each such member of the National Commission must be an American citizen.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ed70146-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/act/1946-07-30/ch700/s4">July 30, 1946, ch. 700, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/60/713">60 Stat. 713</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
